headline: Smurfit Westrock Applies to Cease to be a Reporting Issuer in Certain Canadian Jurisdictions
summary: DUBLIN, December 19, 2024--Smurfit Westrock plc (NYSE: SW, LSE: SWR) ("Smurfit Westrock") announces that it has applied to the Autorité des marchés financiers (the "AMF"), as Smurfit Westrock’s principal securities regulator in Canada, for a decision that it has ceased to be a reporting issuer (the "Order Sought") in Québec, Manitoba and British Columbia (the "Canadian Jurisdictions").
